text: Constance Jablonski is a French model. ==Early life== In 2006, she won Elite Model Look in France. She finished her studies and started modeling two years later. In 2009, she started walking fashion shows, for example for Lanvin, Gucci and Elie Saab. ==Career== Since 2010, she is a spokesmodel for Est√©e Lauder.
